{{Use mdy dates|date=April 2018}} {{Infobox person | name = Clarence Barr | image = | caption = | birth_date = {{birth date|1876|6|8}} | birth_place = [[Omaha, Nebraska]], USA | death_date = June 1968 | death_place = | yearsactive = 1912-1918 | othername = Clarence L. Barr }}
'''Clarence Barr''' (June 8, 1876 &ndash; June 1968) was an American actor of the [[silent film|silent era]]. He appeared in 90 films between 1912 and 1918.
He was born in [[Omaha, Nebraska]].
